            <text for="L119">The screaming</text>
            <text for="L120">The left arm I’ve caught with was sweet <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(When my feelings break down)</span></text>
            <text for="L121">The right arm I’ve swung with was sweet</text>
            <text for="L122">It was sweet</text>
            <text for="L123">It was sweet</text>
            <text for="L124">Even if my mouth with a smile gets torn</text>
            <text for="L125">That’s just fun, so fun <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(My love is overflowing)</span></text>
            <text for="L126">So fun</text>
            <text for="L127">Like burning a brain</text>
            <text for="L128">So fun</text>
            <text for="L129">So fun</text>
            <text for="L130">I’m shaking <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(I can’t stop it)</span></text>
            <text for="L131">I’m shaking</text>
            <text for="L132">So fun</text>
            <text for="L133">So fun</text>
            <text for="L134">Notice my feelings. Why won’t you notice my feelings?</text>
            <text for="L135">I’m overflowing with insanity, how can I stop?</text>
            <text for="L136">Where will I make my way to when my feelings break down?</text>
            <text for="L137">My love is overflowing, I can’t stop it...</text>
            <text for="L138">Red</text>
